    "engine": "knitr",
    "markdown": "---\ntitle: \"Linha-5 Lilás Metrô de São Paulo\"\ndate: \"2024-12-25\"\ncategories: ['data-visualization', 'ggplot2', 'brazil', 'maps']\ndescription: \"Neste post, analiso o fluxo de passageiros na Linha 5-Lilás do metrô de São Paulo. A demanda retornou aos níveis pré-pandemia, com o fluxo nos finais de semana superando em 4,8% os valores de 2019. O fluxo nos dias úteis também se recuperou, superando a média dos valores observados em 2019. Estações com baldeações seguem sendo as mais movimentadas, destacando o papel conector da linha-5.\"\nexecute:\n  message: false\n  warning: false\n  echo: false\n---\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n\n# Linha 5-Lilás do Metrô\n\n-   O número de passageiros transportados pela linha 5-Lilás retornou aos níveis pré-pandemia, com recuperação completa em 2024.\n\n-   Fluxo médio nos finais de semana superou os níveis pré-pandemia, alcançando 104,8% dos valores de 2019. Nos dias úteis o fluxo alcançou 101,8%.\n\n-   Estações mais movimentadas são as com baldeações, reforçando o papel conector da linha-5: Capão Redondo, Santo Amaro e Chácara Klabin.\n\n-   O recorde de passageiros transportados no mês foi registrado ainda antes da pandemia em outubro de 2019, com 16 milhões de passageiros.\n\n### Overview\n\n![](/static/images/spo_metro/line_5_overview.png){fig-align=\"center\"}\n\n### Estações mais movimentadas (últimos 12 meses)\n\n![](/static/images/spo_metro/line_5_station_ranking.png){fig-align=\"center\"}\n\n### Dias de semana\n\n![](/static/images/spo_metro/line_5_pandemic.png){fig-align=\"center\"}\n\n::: panel-tabset\n## Capão Red. - Giovanni\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n![](index_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-2-1.png){width=100%}\n:::\n:::\n\n\n## St Amaro - Alto da Boa Vista\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n![](index_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-3-1.png){width=100%}\n:::\n:::\n\n\n## Borba - Moema\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n![](index_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-4-1.png){width=100%}\n:::\n:::\n\n\n## Hsp SP - AACD\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n![](index_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-5-1.png){width=100%}\n:::\n:::\n\n:::\n\n### Mapa da Linha-5\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"leaflet html-widget html-fill-item\" id=\"htmlwidget-9a479915396d23cb48a6\" style=\"width:100%;height:464px;\"></div>\n<script type=\"application/json\" data-for=\"htmlwidget-9a479915396d23cb48a6\">{\"x\":{\"options\":{\"crs\":{\"crsClass\":\"L.CRS.EPSG3857\",\"code\":null,\"proj4def\":null,\"projectedBounds\":null,\"options\":{}}},\"calls\":[{\"method\":\"addProviderTiles\",\"args\":[\"CartoDB.Positron\",null,null,{\"errorTileUrl\":\"\",\"noWrap\":false,\"detectRetina\":false}]},{\"method\":\"addPolylines\",\"args\":[[[[{\"lng\":[-46.63048644002503,-46.63076652002503,-46.63108728002504,-46.63223928002503,-46.63245204002503,-46.63260936002503,-46.63273104002503,-46.63287180002503,-46.63343736002503,-46.63369260002503,-46.63399104002503,-46.63446624002503,-46.63495800002502,-46.63558332002503,-46.63601028002503,-46.63653408002504,-46.63713960002503,-46.64097648002503,-46.64143800002503,-46.64195460002503,-46.64905164002504,-46.64969064002504,-46.65027456002504,-46.65079332002504,-46.65121488002504,-46.65189204002503,-46.65286080002504,-46.65337956002504,-46.65400812002505,-46.65462444002505,-46.65526884002504,-46.65578544002504,-46.65629484002504,-46.65683376002504,-46.65726756002505,-46.65762828002504,-46.65809052002504,-46.65856068002504,-46.65897504002504,-46.66069080002504,-46.66090788002505,-46.66113108002504,-46.66127292002505,-46.66139460002505,-46.66154868002504,-46.66203468002504,-46.66238784002505,-46.66253364002505,-46.66269384002505,-46.66296024002504,-46.66311720002505,-46.66324140002505,-46.66338396002504,-46.66570380002504,-46.66690008002505,-46.66727268002504,-46.66762944002505,-46.66807116002505,-46.66853340002505,-46.66911732002505,-46.66936032002504,-46.66972644002505,-46.67